OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772118239
OL,3,CScottish government orders grooming
OL,4,Cgangs inquiry headed by expert Alexis
OL,5,CJay
OL,7,FThere will be a public inquiry with
OL,8,Fthe "fullest investigatory powers"
OL,9,Finto grooming gangs in Scotland, the
OL,10,FScottish government has said.
OL,12,FIt launched an independent national
OL,13,Freview of group-based child sexual
OL,14,Fabuse and exploitation in December,
OL,15,Fwhich the government said would help
OL,16,Fin deciding whether a public inquiry
OL,17,Fwould be necessary.
OL,26,@pD@EOUpD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
