FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772118239
OL,3,CScottish government orders grooming
OL,4,Cgangs inquiry headed by expert Alexis
OL,5,CJay
OL,7,FThe first minister and justice
OL,8,Fsecretary were under continued
OL,9,Fpressure to launch an inquiry, similar
OL,10,Fto the one already underway in
OL,11,FEngland, as more victims in Scotland
OL,12,Fcame forward.
OL,14,FIn December, ITV News spoke to
OL,15,F'Taylor', who told us that she was
OL,16,Fsexually abused by a group of
OL,17,FPakistani men while growing up in the
OL,18,Fcare system in the West of Scotland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772118239
OL,3,CScottish government orders grooming
OL,4,Cgangs inquiry headed by expert Alexis
OL,5,CJay
OL,7,FAfter hearing her story, two more
OL,8,Fwomen came forward saying they were
OL,9,Falso preyed upon and abused by groups
OL,10,Fof men while they were young girls in
OL,11,Fthe care system in Glasgow.
OL,13,FThe inquiry will be chaired by
OL,14,FProfessor Alexis Jay, who led the
OL,15,Finquiry into sexual exploitation in
OL,16,FRotherham and the Independent Inquiry
OL,17,Finto Child Sexual Abuse in 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772118239
OL,3,CScottish government orders grooming
OL,4,Cgangs inquiry headed by expert Alexis
OL,5,CJay
OL,7,FEducation Secretary Jenny Gilruth said
OL,8,FProf Jay has "unrivalled experience"
OL,9,Fof chairing inquiries into child
OL,10,Fsexual abuse and exploitation, as well
OL,11,Fas "vast experience" of child
OL,12,Fprotection issues in more than 30
OL,13,Fyears of professional experience in
OL,14,Fsocial work.
OL,16,FAs well as the public inquiry, the
OL,17,FScottish government also plans to
OL,18,Festablish a "Truth Project" to allow
OL,19,Fvictims and survivors of childhood
OL,20,Fsexual abuse and exploitation to tell
OL,21,Ftheir stories.
OL,26,@pD@NOUpD@dO]sD@DOUsD@TO]zD@MOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772118239
OL,3,CScottish government orders grooming
OL,4,Cgangs inquiry headed by expert Alexis
OL,5,CJay
OL,7,FAnnouncing the plans, Ms Gilruth told
OL,8,FHolyrood the decision to establish the
OL,9,Finquiry had not been taken lightly,
OL,10,Fgiven the cost to the public purse.
OL,12,FWhile the Scottish Child Abuse
OL,13,FInquiry, which was established by the
OL,14,FScottish government in 2015, is to
OL,15,Flook at similar issues, Ms Gilruth
OL,16,Fsaid this had a broader remit, and the
OL,17,Fnew inquiry will "focus specifically
OL,18,Fon group-based child abuse and
OL,19,Fexploitation".
OL,26,@yD@ROU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772118239
OL,3,CScottish government orders grooming
OL,4,Cgangs inquiry headed by expert Alexis
OL,5,CJay
OL,7,FThe new inquiry is "critical" in
OL,8,F"encouraging openness and
OL,9,Fparticipation from victims and
OL,10,Fsurvivors", the minister added.
OL,12,FShe said: "It will focus on the
OL,13,Fpotential prevalence of group-based
OL,14,Fabuse now and in the more recent past.
OL,16,F"The inquiry will, therefore, have the
OL,17,Ffullest investigatory powers required."
OL,19,FThe Scottish government had previously
OL,20,Fsaid there was not enough evidence to
OL,21,Fjustify such an inquiry in Scotland.
OL,26,@oD@TOUoD@]O]pD@AOUrD@JO]tD@KOUxD@AOUyD@
